<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-129af9c5455ffcae9f468185aea34654bb3dcea9">The Heavy Crossbow of Umbar (x6) (+18,+18)</h2>
<em>A great brazen arbalest with arms of gleaming steel, shooting quarrels with speed and power for those brave enough to risk betrayal.</em> <p>
It can be activated for magic arrow (10d10) every 20+d20 turns if it is being worn. It increases your strength and constitution by 2. It provides resistance to electricity, light, dark and blindness. It fires missiles with extra might. It aggravates nearby creatures. 
</p>
